data.description: Beautiful brick ranch with great bones that has been updated and ready for new owners, located in a well established neighborhood, this spacious home offers 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, 3 family areas for entertaining and a 2 car garage, low maintenance outside with  it being brick, rock landscaping and large concrete back yard, great for those family gatherings, covered patios front and back for your morning coffee, no HOA, roof was replaced in 2021, recently a new sewer line installed,  this home is conveniently located to restaurants, shopping and main highways, agent related to seller, make your appointment to see it today!
